Midweek Prettiness, Paradoxe @pradabeauty ✨️

Prada Paradoxe* is a sweet, warm, fruity floral fragrance, smells very feminine and unique. The beautiful blend of neroli and jasmine notes makes it perfect for day and night and lasts all day. 
#pradaparadoxe

#diptyqueparisgiftedme the perfect candles for 'tis season ✨️ @diptyque

Limited Edition festive candles are adorned with white, gold, and silver stars on Diptyque's map of stars to enhance the vivid color of the wax. They are stunning on display, and the stars of the vessels glow in the dark.

Etincelles/ Spark Candle has a chocolate/ woody aroma and smells sweet, fresh, and warm. Perfect festive scent!

Neige/ Snow candle diffuses a soft heliotrope, and white musk reminds me of a clean snowy winter morning. It is delicate, clean, and perfect for the holiday season.

Iconic Baies is gorgeous with a blend of floral and fruity ( blackcurrant, berries, and roses ) and is my favorite scent from Diptyque.

It is intoxicating, warm, fruity, and very addictive and perfect for spring/ summer 🫶🏽

@tatcha Ritual ft. New Silk Serum 🫶🏽💜

Tatcha's new silk serum is a potent retinol alternative with skin-soothing benefits and is gentle enough to use daily. It contains silk protein, Hadasei-3 complex, cranberry extract, and sea fennel.

The formula is lightweight, absorbs beautifully onto the skin, and the soft botanical aroma feels luxurious.
I have been using the serum for a few days AM/PM, and it instantly left me feeling firmer and more nourished. I love pairing it with silk cream for hydrated, dewy, plumped skin.

Vinoperfect @caudalie 🍇

Caudalie is one of my favorite skincare brands, and the Vinpoerfect range is a staple in my skincare routine. The vinoperfect serum is 62x more effective than vitamin C, is non-irritating, helps reduce the PIH, and evens the skin tone.
Caudalie recently added a new Brightening Eye cream to this range, formulated with viniferine caffeine and niacinamide, targets to correct blue, purple, brown, and black dark circles for a brighter eye contour. The texture of the eye cream is so lightweight, feels cooling, deeply hydrating, and absorbs instantly. The cooling ceramic applicator tip is perfect for gently massaging the eye area. Have you tried it yet?

#eyeconic #vinoperfect #caudalie @caudalieus

Celebrating 25 years of  @chantecaille with The Iconic 5 🫶🏽

Chantecaille is a beautiful brand that creates cutting-edge, luxurious skincare and makeup products that work with a give-back conservation commitment.

Chantecaille's iconic five formulas are the epitome of their botanical brilliance.

Pure Rosewater ( launched in 2001 ) is a multi-tasking toner that replenishes moisture and soothes after cleansing.

Bio Lifting Serum ( launched 2011) is a potent serum with anti-aging benefits.

Future Skin Foundation  ( launched in 1999 ) is lightweight, blends like a dream, and leaves the skin looking natural & beautiful.

Faux Cils Longest Lash Mascara lengthens and separates leashes beautifully.

Lip Veil ( launched in 2018 ) lipsticks are creamy, luxurious, and feel light and comfortable on the lips.

Thank you, @Chantecaille, for your beautiful products and dedication to supporting conservative partners to bring awareness!! 🐘

LE BAUME 🤍 
@diorbeauty @diorbeautylovers 

Le Baume is an ultra-compact, multi-purpose treatment that helps hydrate and soothe dry areas of the hands, lips, and body. It has quite a unique formula, super hydrating but spreads and absorbs fast. The chic compact design makes it the perfect on-the-go hydrator.

Nu Bare Look skin tint is a makeup skincare hybrid infused with hyaluronic acid, glycerin, and brightening mallow. The formula feels lightweight and gives a natural finish that lasts all day. It was my go-to face makeup in the summer, and I’m excited to continue using it into the colder months for an instant filtered look and an extra layer of hydration.  

Nu Lip and Cheeky Balm Tint have a creamy formula that blends seamlessly for a natural-looking flush of hydrating, lightweight color on both cheeks and lips. They come in three shades - a plum, a red, and a peach - and are perfect for those #STRAWBERRYMAKEUP days. 

YSL candy glaze lip gloss feels nourishing and hydrating on the lips, and its easy melt-on color gives a gorgeous high shine. And the smell is delicious. 

Crusher in Bleu Enigmatique glides onto eyelids, water, and smudge-proof, and stays put. 

@YSLBEAUTY, #YSLBEAUTY #GIFTEDBYYSLBEAUTY #lashckash #clash200

@tatcha favorites 🤍 

The indigo cleansing balm is my new favorite from Tatcha. The texture is so soft, sinks quickly into the skin, and effortlessly removes even the most stubborn matte lipstick and mascara. It left my skin looking squeaky clean, plump with hydration, and notably more soothed than other face washes.  

The camellia cleansing oil is a rich antioxidant cleansing oil, feels silky and works effortlessly to remove makeup and dirt. Leaves skin balanced and hydrated. 

The Rice polish has a powder formula which turns into the softest foam when mixed with water and feels luxurious on the skin. Leaves skin soft and supple. 

The essence has a lightweight watery formula and instantly hydrate the skin leaving it with a beautiful glow. 

The silk cream is a rich, lightweight gel-cream moisturizer, feels smoothing and nourishing on the skin.

Fall lineup courtesy of @armani.beauty✨️🍂

The silk concealer is super hydrating, blendable, and gives an airbrush finish. Also, it contains caffeine and vitamin E to reduce undereye puffiness and brighten the eye area. 

The luminous silk primer is a perfect base, a super hydrating formula, and melts into the skin during application while blurring imperfections.
